</li>
<li id="cite_note-45">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-45">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The Latin legend reads: <small>TANTO NOMINI NULLUM PAR ELOGIUM</small> ("So great a name (has) no adequate praise" or "No <a href="/wiki/Eulogy" title="Eulogy">eulogy</a> (would be) a match for such a great name" or "There is no praise equal to so great a name.")</span>
